
These are the 'x'tra emotions of the mini guilds, so you must put
an 'x' before the adjective to use them.  Xample?  xarch or xtwirl.

  arch            bashful          blush            boggle
  cheer           cold             coo              cool
  giggle          giggle2          jump             kiss
  mock            scoff            shy              smile
  smolder         spaz             twirl            wonder
  wry


NEW EMOTIONS

  dejected        heartbreak       hopeful          hum
  innocent        manic            relax


Have fun with these, and if there are any more that
you would like to see, mail me.
                                                     -- Saber
